latestPosts.caption: This post was long overdue! When your school friend trusts and believes in you and opens up the doors to do an art workshop with her friends….trust me, thats when nervousness sets in :). @nityabhalla thank you for all of that and much more❤️. If only you were so good to me back in school😬. “The Journey Within” is a three part concept designed to visit yourself - do you wear your heart on your sleeve? Or do you think more practically? Are you an intuitive person? Or do you just go with the flow of the day? There is just so much to us than we actually realise. We also had a little 9 year old visiting this journey - and how delightful her journey is! 💖 Such a lovely bunch @nityabhalla @_deeglowvibes_  @smrutishradhanjali and a happy night spent together. Much love to this bunch of lively people 🤗 #visualart
